caption.title: Structural analysis of clade-specific amino acid residues.
caption.p: Threonine 155 in the E1 protein (magenta) and Serine 185 in the E2 protein (green) were visualized on the three-dimensional hetero-multimeric structure (PDB: 3J2W). The colored insets show a magnified view of the regions surrounding T155 and S185 (magenta and green, respectively).
